<p><strong>Yeah, I totally get that. I believe in capitalism too especially when it comes to small business. But big tech? Theyâ€™re not customer centric at all. Like <a href="https://mastiffsystems.com/blog/On-Linux-VMware-and-Broadcom/">VMWare</a> they make moves that benefit shareholders, not customers. Honestly, modern big tech often feels anti good customer experience.</strong></p>

